  <compounddef id="path_8hpp" kind="file" language="C++">
    <compoundname>path.hpp</compoundname>
    <innerclass refid="classhmap_1_1Path" prot="public">hmap::Path</innerclass>
    <innernamespace refid="namespacehmap">hmap</innernamespace>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Path class for manipulating and analyzing paths in 2D space. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This file defines the <computeroutput>Path</computeroutput> class, which extends the <computeroutput>Cloud</computeroutput> class to provide functionalities specific to paths. The <computeroutput>Path</computeroutput> class includes methods for creating, manipulating, and analyzing paths, including smoothing the path with various curves, resampling, and performing operations like meandering and fractalizing.</para>
